name: Donald's Dino Bash Flotilla
desc: Donald and his friends take Donald’s Dino Bash to the Discovery River. Keep an eye out for their party boat throughout the day.

name: Mickey and Friends Flotilla
desc: Ready for a brand-new adventure, Mickey and his friends set sail on the Discovery River.

name: Discovery Island Drummers Flotilla
desc: The Discovery Island Drummers take their music to the water, performing live as they sail around the Discovery River.

name: Feathered Friends in Flight!
desc: Even More Magic – As You Wish! Let Disney Genie service summon the attractions, entertainment and dining you love most.

name: Disney Junior Play and Dance!
desc: Join Doc McStuffins, Vampirina, Timon and Mickey for a high-energy musical celebration.

name: The Hollywood Holiday Tower Hotel
desc: See how holiday magic transforms the famous Hollywood Tower Hotel into a Muppets’ gingerbread masterpiece, a Toy Story toy hotel, a snowy corner of Arendelle and a Dickensian village from Mickey’s Christmas Carol.

name: Holiday Entertainment at Disney Springs
desc: Create new memories, start cherished traditions and spend quality time with loved ones at Disney Springs this holiday season. Share in the joy of seasonal experiences, including:Let It Snow! Snow flurries are in the forecast in Town Center at Disney Springs! Throughout the evening, behold a magical snowfall that’s sure to add a touch of wonder to your visit.DJs Enjoy lively entertainment at Waterside Stage, where DJs will keep the tunes flowing throughout the day.Performers In the evening, be on the lookout for toy soldier stilt-walkers and snowflake skaters throughout Disney Springs.

name: Disney Springs Christmas Tree Stroll & Map Activity presented by AdventHealth
Temporarily Unavailable Entertainment at Walt Disney World Resort
desc: While entertainment awaits you at Walt Disney World Resort, some experiences are temporarily unavailable in order to accommodate physical distancing. Learn about updated experiences.

name: Harmonious - New!
desc: Experience this nighttime spectacular and discover how Disney music and stories have the power to bring people together.

name: Disney KiteTails - New!
desc: Watch as favorite Disney characters take to the sky for an all-new performance during The World’s Most Magical Celebration!

name: Disney Enchantment - New!
desc: Behold a brand-new nighttime fireworks spectacular that empowers you to believe in yourself and in magic.

name: Beacons of Magic - New!
desc: The World’s Most Magical Celebration will light up with wonder as the theme park icons are transformed into Beacons of Magic, beckoning all to come and celebrate.Available seasonally on select nights. Images are artist concepts only.

name: Beauty & The Beast Live on Stage
desc: Relive the romance and magic of a tale as old as time in a lavish Broadway-style musical version of Beauty and the Beast.

name: Jellyrolls
desc: Let the good times roll at this lively piano bar for Guests over 21 with dueling pianos and audience sing-alongs.

name: Music of Mexico
desc: Sway to exuberant mariachi music as you catch a performance by this spirited band.

name: Matsuriza
desc: Bang the Drums  Feel the rhythm as this group of traditional Japanese drummers performs intricate musical arrangements on giant drums in a dazzling display of pure physical stamina.Japanese Taiko drums have been enthralling audiences for years in religious ceremonies, festivals and even on battlefields as soldiers prayed for victory. Come witness the thrill of Taiko for yourself!

name: Sergio
desc: Clowning Around  As you stroll the charming piazza at the Italy Pavilion, stop and enjoy the antics and impressive skills of our resident juggler. Cheer loud enough and he may invite you to become part of the act!

name: Voices of Liberty
desc: Listen as the Voices of Liberty fill the rotunda of The American Adventure Pavilion with the pristine harmonies that celebrate the American experience.

name: Fantasmic! - Returning 2022!
desc: Be there as the forces of good and evil battle it out in Mickey’s dream during this extravagant open-air nighttime musical.

name: The Tree of Life: A Beacon of Magic
desc: A warm and glorious light emanates from the Tree of Life, as enchanted fireflies gather to call forth the magic of nature.

name: Spaceship Earth: A Beacon of Magic
desc: Lights shine from within Spaceship Earth’s reflective panels as stardust emerges to symbolize beacons of possibility and optimism.

name: The Hollywood Tower Hotel: A Beacon of Magic
desc: The iconic Hollywood Tower Hotel glitters with EARidescence, evoking the glimmer and shimmer of the golden age of imagination and adventure.

name: Cinderella Castle: A Beacon of Magic
desc: Cinderella Castle illuminates the park with a dazzling glow that sparkles with pixie dust.

name: Disney Friends Cavalcade
desc: Disney Friends CavalcadeYour favorite Disney pals invite you to celebrate a magical day along the parade route.

name: Disney Adventure Friends Cavalcade
desc: Sing and Dance with Friends  A new cavalcade is coming your way! Join us along the parade route—from Frontierland through Liberty Square down Main Street, U.S.A—as an exciting line up of Characters embark on a journey through park.In fact, Disney Adventure Friends Cavalcade will feature the most characters of any cavalcade to date, including:Nick and Judy from ZootopiaBaloo and King Louie from The Jungle BookJosé Carioca and Panchito from The Three CaballerosMiguel from CocoMerida from BraveMoana from MoanaThe IncrediblesPlus, so many more!!Don’t miss this chance to see some of your Disney favorites in action! This cavalcade will be appearing multiple times throughout the day at Magic Kingdom Park. Check your My Disney Experience app for showtimes.

name: Finding Nemo: The Big Blue... and Beyond! - Now Open!
desc: Dive into a spectacular stage show—filled with puppets, singers and other performers—set in the underwater world of Disney and Pixar’s Finding Nemo.

name: Goofy and Pals Set Sail
desc: Leaving their posts at Donald’s Dino Bash, Goofy and his Pals cruise down the Discovery River.

name: Sighting on Tower of Terror Balcony
Meet Chip and Dale in Storybook Circus
Command Performance
desc: Rock out with Command Performance as they perform British rock from the 1960s through 1990s in the United Kingdom gazebo.

name: Discovery River Cruise - Pocahontas
desc: Gather your group to see beloved Characters from the Disney animated film, Pocahontas, and wave to them as they cruise along Discovery River.
